          "<b>5. Lifestyle Changes</b>",
          "The fifth strategy that naturopathy adopts to alleviate and manage knee pain is lifestyle changes. This encompasses relaxation techniques, getting adequate sleep, quitting smoking, avoiding activities that put too much strain on the knees, etc. Knee discomfort can also be reduced by applying ergonomic concepts to regular tasks. Doctors at VSR Vriksha Nature Cure Centre, the <b><a href=\"https://vsrvriksha.com/\">best naturopathy center in Hyderabad</a></b> recommend such a holistic approach to knee pain management.",
          "<b>6. Hot/Cold Compress or Knee Packs</b>",
          "If you are experiencing achy joints due to inflammation, applying a hot/cold compress or knee packs to the painful area can bring ample relief.",
